	<h1 class="title">为纪念一战百年，英国人种上88万朵虞美人</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/1329/small/1329.jpg?1418779602" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">胡莹 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-08-06 08:20:18 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/1742/medium/1742.jpg?1436645433" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


